Don't mind my first PHP project. It's a simple landing page with admin/user capabilities (formerly known as DLi).

Basic:
- Register
- Registration - Email Verification
- Sign In
- Sign In - Email Code Verification
- New User Welcome Modal - Complete Profile
- Update Profile
- Change-Password (password reset from account settings)
- Send Email
- Upload Image
- Edit Image (current image will be replaced and deleted in DB and directory)
- Search Bar
- Logout
- Forgot-Password (password reset from sign-in page)

Admin:
- Everything in Basic
- Analytics
- Activity & Email Log
- Account Management - Add/Edit/Delete User

Currently Logging:
- Registration
- Sign In
- Log Out
- Update Profile
- Add User
- Delete User
- Email

Pending:
- Profile Page
- Internal-Messaging System
